# IBAN-style mod-97 check (simplified to digit string).
*mod97(digits as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    r is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        r is (r * 10 + digits.get(i)) % 97
        i is i + 1
    r

*main
    d is vec()
    d.push(1)
    d.push(2)
    d.push(3)
    d.push(4)
    d.push(5)
    d.push(6)
    d.push(7)
    log mod97(d, 7)
